      "title": "Police seek public assistance to identify 72 suspects",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Police have sought public assistance to identify 72 suspects who trespassed into the Presidential Secretariat and damaged its property.",
        "In a statement, the police said that the Colombo North Division Criminal Investigation Department is conducting investigations into the matter.",
        "Photographs of the suspects have are below, and public have been requested to grant any information regarding the relevant suspects via 0112083049, 0756371563, the hotline 1997 or via WhatsApp."
      ],
